1410
01:01:53,737 --> 01:01:55,166
- One jjajangmyeon.
- What?

1411
01:01:55,167 --> 01:01:57,607
- One jjajangmyeon.
- One jjajangmyeon? Okay.

1412
01:01:57,837 --> 01:02:00,507
Chef Yoo Bang Nyeong keeps making something over there.

1413
01:02:01,347 --> 01:02:04,047
