1414
01:02:04,317 --> 01:02:05,317
(Min's)

1415
01:02:05,318 --> 01:02:06,377
One set.

1416
01:02:08,387 --> 01:02:10,517
My heart is pounding.

1417
01:02:11,217 --> 01:02:12,756
We're totally crushing the orders.

1418
01:02:12,757 --> 01:02:14,126
