1419
01:02:14,127 --> 01:02:15,127
It's the best.

1420
01:02:19,797 --> 01:02:21,827
We now have the 15th restaurant...

1421
01:02:22,097 --> 01:02:25,367
to survive the 1,000-dollar sales race.

1422
01:02:26,169 --> 01:02:27,408
We now have the 15th restaurant...

1423
01:02:27,409 --> 01:02:29,469
