- Min's.

1441
01:03:23,729 --> 01:03:24,799
Sunlin.

1442
01:03:25,329 --> 01:03:26,529
Arirang House.

1443
01:03:27,629 --> 01:03:28,699
Min's.

1444
01:03:29,469 --> 01:03:30,869
Everything About Tteokbokki.

1445
01:03:31,911 --> 01:03:33,169
Agungi.

1446
