1481
01:05:00,530 --> 01:05:02,900
- Pork galbi.
- Galbi sounds good.

1482
01:05:03,630 --> 01:05:05,099
- Should we order one?
- There are only a few left.

1483
01:05:05,100 --> 01:05:06,300
