- Should we order one?

1484
01:05:06,430 --> 01:05:07,940
Come and enjoy pork galbi.

1485
01:05:08,370 --> 01:05:09,970
Please enjoy your food!

1486
01:05:10,740 --> 01:05:12,769
- What do you want to eat?
- They have things like this.

1487
01:05:12,770 --> 01:05:13,879
I know. It looks good.

1488
01:05:13,880 --> 01:05:15,209
- Should we order this one?
- They have a set meal.

1489
01:05:15,210 --> 01:05:17,080
- This one?
- Yes, I like it.

1490
01:05:17,950 --> 01:05:19,149
Let's eat pork galbi.

1491
01:05:19,150 --> 01:05:21,080
(1 butter pork galbi, 19 dollars)

1492
01:05:21,380 --> 01:05:23,850
- Do you want butter pork galbi?
- Yes. Let's eat this.

1493
01:05:24,250 --> 01:05:26,649
With only a few restaurants available, we will get busier.

1494
01:05:26,650 --> 01:05:27,860
