1505
01:05:55,980 --> 01:05:57,790
We're going to make a comeback.

1506
01:05:57,850 --> 01:05:59,749
The weather is quite chilly now.

1507
01:05:59,750 --> 01:06:01,790
People will definitely line up for some soup curry.

1508
01:06:02,090 --> 01:06:03,160
