1510
01:06:07,660 --> 01:06:10,870
Try the curry a little. It will warm up your body.

1511
01:06:11,230 --> 01:06:12,270
There you go.

1512
01:06:12,870 --> 01:06:13,870
It's not spicy.

1513
01:06:13,871 --> 01:06:15,170
