1551
01:07:51,900 --> 01:07:53,130
He's cooking.

1552
01:07:53,470 --> 01:07:55,040
There's a whole crowd of people standing there.

1553
01:07:55,670 --> 01:07:57,910
- Look at Sunlin.
- What? Really?

1554
01:07:58,540 --> 01:08:00,070
He's cooking now.

1555
01:08:00,940 --> 01:08:02,280
One more nanja wanseu.

1556
01:08:02,780 --> 01:08:04,110
- One nanja wanseu?
- Yes.

1557
01:08:04,510 --> 01:08:06,010
Dad, one nanja wanseu.

1558
01:08:06,310 --> 01:08:08,420
- Okay.
- We got one more order.

1559
01:08:15,360 --> 01:08:16,920
Let's give it a shot.

1560
01:08:17,860 --> 01:08:19,260
We never know how it will turn out.

1561
01:08:20,390 --> 01:08:21,930
The restaurant next to us...

1562
01:08:22,400 --> 01:08:23,900
