1563
01:08:25,570 --> 01:08:26,930
Good luck, Mr. Kim!

1564
01:08:27,940 --> 01:08:30,570
We have to serve three servings of this.

1565
01:08:31,070 --> 01:08:32,810
No. There's more. Gosh, we're in trouble.

1566
01:08:33,410 --> 01:08:36,640
Since the orders kept flooding in,

1567
01:08:36,880 --> 01:08:38,210
I thought we would stand a chance...

1568
01:08:38,910 --> 01:08:41,619
