1569
01:08:41,620 --> 01:08:43,180
So I focused only on cooking.

1570
01:08:44,820 --> 01:08:46,720
If we knock out the orders quickly, we can sell a lot.

1571
01:08:52,390 --> 01:08:53,660
Number 1043.

1572
01:08:54,260 --> 01:08:55,260
Enjoy your food.

1573
01:08:56,160 --> 01:08:57,700
- I should keep frying, right?
- Yes.

1574
01:09:00,840 --> 01:09:02,299
He spent the whole day doing nothing but frying.

1575
01:09:02,300 --> 01:09:04,869
It looks so good even through the screen.

1576
01:09:04,870 --> 01:09:07,580
- And he cooked tteokbokki all day.
- I know.

1577
01:09:07,880 --> 01:09:09,740
(Only tteokbokki)

1578
01:09:09,780 --> 01:09:11,750
(Only fritters)

1579
01:09:11,780 --> 01:09:16,279
(Still like a stone, busy like a honeybee)

1580
01:09:16,280 --> 01:09:18,249
(The mountain of piled-up fritters...)

1581
01:09:18,250 --> 01:09:20,890
