1582
01:09:21,320 --> 01:09:22,890
Thank you.

1583
01:09:23,620 --> 01:09:24,759
Enjoy your food.

1584
01:09:24,760 --> 01:09:26,760
(Everything About Tteokbokki steadily builds up their sales.)

1585
01:09:29,160 --> 01:09:31,300
Arirang House. Bossam.

1586
01:09:32,270 --> 01:09:33,600
It's bossam.

1587
01:09:34,370 --> 01:09:35,540
If we order this,

1588
01:09:35,770 --> 01:09:37,640
