1589
01:09:38,140 --> 01:09:39,910
- Let's order one.
- One?

1590
01:09:40,670 --> 01:09:42,710
One medium bossam and kimchi.

1591
01:09:43,080 --> 01:09:44,110
Okay.

1592
01:09:44,550 --> 01:09:47,450
The makguksu and rice balls were add-on items earlier,

1593
01:09:48,020 --> 01:09:49,620
but the time was ticking away,

1594
01:09:50,050 --> 01:09:52,890
and I felt like I had to do something.

1595
01:09:53,350 --> 01:09:54,960
Should we change the makguksu to free?

1596
01:09:55,960 --> 01:09:57,759
In a desperate attempt to get at least one more order,

1597
01:09:57,760 --> 01:09:59,690
I changed all the add-on items to free...

1598
01:09:59,830 --> 01:10:01,800
