1645
01:12:14,730 --> 01:12:16,730
The Time Race is now over.

1646
01:12:18,030 --> 01:12:19,070
Ten.

1647
01:12:19,830 --> 01:12:20,840
Nine.

1648
01:12:21,840 --> 01:12:22,870
Eight.

1649
01:12:23,840 --> 01:12:24,870
Seven.

1650
01:12:25,810 --> 01:12:26,810
Six.

1651
01:12:27,680 --> 01:12:28,680
Five.

1652
01:12:29,840 --> 01:12:30,840
Four.

1653
01:12:31,750 --> 01:12:32,750
Three.

1654
01:12:33,550 --> 01:12:34,550
Two.

1655
01:12:35,550 --> 01:12:36,580
One.

1656
01:12:40,150 --> 01:12:42,390
That sound is traumatizing me.

1657
01:12:45,060 --> 01:12:47,600
Dinner business is now over.

1658
01:12:48,830 --> 01:12:50,400
The final five teams...

1659
01:12:51,030 --> 01:12:54,200
