1660
01:12:57,140 --> 01:12:58,270
Well done.

1661
01:12:58,440 --> 01:12:59,910
- What?
- You did great.

1662
01:13:00,410 --> 01:13:01,440
Oh, yes.

1663
01:13:02,580 --> 01:13:04,880
- Aren't your legs tired?
- No.

1664
01:13:07,150 --> 01:13:08,350
We still did our best.

1665
01:13:13,150 --> 01:13:14,489
(Agungi)

1666
01:13:14,490 --> 01:13:15,490
That was close.

1667
01:13:18,060 --> 01:13:19,390
It's like a slaughterhouse.

1668
01:13:21,100 --> 01:13:22,460
We're on the verge of surviving or getting eliminated.

1669
01:13:23,600 --> 01:13:25,770
But we did our best.

1670
01:13:26,030 --> 01:13:27,470
We did everything we could.

1671
01:13:28,200 --> 01:13:29,570
