1672
01:13:30,870 --> 01:13:33,040
We have nothing to lose.

1673
01:13:33,110 --> 01:13:35,440
If we make it in top 18, we won't be eliminated.

1674
01:13:35,880 --> 01:13:37,510
I had a feeling...

1675
01:13:38,550 --> 01:13:40,910
Chef Kim Min Seong sold...

1676
01:13:41,680 --> 01:13:44,350
