1678
01:13:48,260 --> 01:13:49,459
(Bossam and 3 kinds of kimchi for 38 dollars)

1679
01:13:49,460 --> 01:13:50,720
Whereas Chef Kim Min Seong...

1680
01:13:51,190 --> 01:13:53,360
