1684
01:14:03,900 --> 01:14:05,070
I don't think it was bad.

1685
01:14:06,640 --> 01:14:08,410
I probably ranked after Sunlin.

1686
01:14:08,710 --> 01:14:10,680
Anyway, I don't think I got eliminated.

1687
01:14:11,750 --> 01:14:12,780
Eighteenth.

1688
01:14:13,550 --> 01:14:14,550
Seventeenth.

1689
01:14:15,850 --> 01:14:17,720
I'm expecting 19th.

1690
01:14:18,520 --> 01:14:21,920
