1698
01:14:47,450 --> 01:14:48,520
Excellent.

1699
01:14:49,020 --> 01:14:50,419
Second place, Bol A Bol.

1700
01:14:50,420 --> 01:14:52,319
(2nd place, Bol A Bol, 96 minutes to reach 1,000 dollars)

1701
01:14:52,320 --> 01:14:53,320
Chef.

1702
01:14:53,321 --> 01:14:55,119
Third place, The Star In My Heart.

1703
01:14:55,120 --> 01:14:57,730
(3rd place, The Star In My Heart, 141 minutes to reach 1,000 dollars)

1704
01:14:57,890 --> 01:14:59,459
Fourth place, Hohyunghojae.

1705
01:14:59,460 --> 01:15:01,429
(4th place, Hohyunghojae, 157 minutes to reach 1,000 dollars)

1706
01:15:01,430 --> 01:15:02,829
Fifth place, HunGry.

1707
01:15:02,830 --> 01:15:05,729
