1718
01:15:18,680 --> 01:15:20,150
Eleventh place, Extraordinary Couple.

1719
01:15:20,780 --> 01:15:22,119
Twelfth place, Koony.

1720
01:15:22,120 --> 01:15:23,279
(12th place, Koony, 203 minutes to reach 1,000 dollars)

1721
01:15:23,280 --> 01:15:25,020
Thirteenth place, Wolfie's.

1722
01:15:25,750 --> 01:15:27,290
Fourteenth place, Gyeol.

1723
01:15:28,220 --> 01:15:30,159
Fifteenth place goes to Ma Restaurant.

1724
01:15:30,160 --> 01:15:32,089
